<pb n="1115b" ed="T" xml:id="T12.0393.1115b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="1115b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="1115b02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 393</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="1115b03" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115014">（佛說）＋迦【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115014">迦【大】，佛說迦【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1115014"><lem wit="【大】">迦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛說迦</rdg></app>葉赴佛<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115015">〔般〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115015">般【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1115015"><lem wit="【大】">般</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>涅槃經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="1115b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1115b05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">東晉<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115016" resp="Taisho">〔西域沙門〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115016" resp="CBETA">西域沙門【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115016"><lem wit="【大】">西域沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="1115b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1115b0601">昔佛在世時，摩訶迦葉於諸比丘中最長年
<lb n="1115b07" ed="T"/>高，才明智慧，其身亦有金色相好；佛每說法，
<lb n="1115b08" ed="T"/>常與其對坐，人民見之或呼為佛師。於是迦
<lb ed="T" n="1115b09"/>葉乃辭佛，到伊<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115017" resp="Taisho">篩梨＝蒢黎【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">篩梨【大】，蒢黎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115017"><lem wit="【大】">篩梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蒢黎</rdg></app>山中。一山名普能，周旋
<lb ed="T" n="1115b10"/>數千里，去舍衛國二萬六千里，多出七寶，甘
<lb n="1115b11" ed="T"/>果不<note n="1115018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訾＝貲【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115018">訾【大】，貲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115018"><lem wit="【大】">訾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貲</rdg></app>，名香、好藥、栴檀三種：其一種芳香，一
<lb n="1115b12" ed="T"/>種治人百病，一種可用染五色。眾香雜藥不
<lb ed="T" n="1115b13"/>可稱數。亦有走翔鳥獸——師子、<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115019">虎＝犲【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虎【大】，犲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115019"><lem wit="【大】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">犲</rdg></app>、狼、白象、騏驎、
<lb n="1115b14" ed="T"/>朱<note resp="Taisho" n="1115020" place="foot text" type="orig">雀＝鳥【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115020" type="mod">雀【大】，鳥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115020"><lem wit="【大】">雀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鳥</rdg></app>、鳳凰。或有清淨異學道士。時有方石平
<lb ed="T" n="1115b15"/>正，其色如琉璃，縱廣百二十里，奇樹蔭涼、華
<lb n="1115b16" ed="T"/>葉五色，冬夏茂盛列生石上。迦葉前後教授
<lb n="1115b17" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" n="1115021" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝一【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115021" resp="CBETA">二【大】，一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115021"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>千弟子，皆清淨高行得羅漢者，常坐此石
<lb ed="T" n="1115b18"/><note resp="Taisho" n="1115022" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115022" resp="CBETA">上【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦經行道。又有清淨甘<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115023" resp="Taisho">香＝果【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115023" type="mod">香【大】，果【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115023"><lem wit="【大】">香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">果</rdg></app>泉水，周旋
<lb ed="T" n="1115b19"/><note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115024">四＝三【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115024" resp="CBETA">四【大】，三【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115024"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">三</rdg></app>十里，其<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115025" resp="Taisho">水中則有優曇華＝側生優曇華青蓮華【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115025" resp="CBETA">水中則有優曇華【大】，側生優曇華青蓮華【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115025"><lem wit="【大】">水中則有優曇華</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">側生優曇華青蓮華</rdg></app>，紺色華、紅色
<lb ed="T" n="1115b20"/>華、紫色華。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1115b2005" rend="inline">迦葉弟子七人，同夕得夢：其一比
<lb ed="T" n="1115b21"/>丘，夢見<note n="1115026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115026">其【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115026"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>所坐方石中央分破，樹皆根拔；復
<lb ed="T" n="1115b22"/>一比丘夢見四十里泉水皆乾竭，華悉零落；一
<lb n="1115b23" ed="T"/>比丘夢見拘羅邊坐皆傾毀；一比丘夢<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115027" resp="Taisho">〔見〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115027" type="mod">見【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115027"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>閻
<lb n="1115b24" ed="T"/>浮利地皆傾陷；一比丘夢見須彌山崩；一比
<lb ed="T" n="1115b25"/>丘夢見金輪王薨；一比丘夢見日月墮地，天
<lb n="1115b26" ed="T"/>下失明。晨起各以所夢啟迦葉。迦葉告言：「我
<lb ed="T" n="1115b27"/>曹前見光明，地時大動，卿等復得是夢，佛將
<lb ed="T" n="1115b28"/>般泥洹。」即勅諸弟子往赴俱夷那竭國。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1115b2816">道見
<lb ed="T" n="1115b29"/><note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115028" resp="Taisho">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115028">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115028"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>婆羅門，持文陀羅華。迦葉即問言：「卿從
<pb ed="T" n="1115c" xml:id="T12.0393.1115c"/>
<lb n="1115c01" ed="T"/>何來？欲何所至？那得是天華？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1115c0112">答言：「我從<note n="1115029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔俱夷〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俱夷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115029"><lem wit="【大】">俱
<lb ed="T" n="1115c02"/>夷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>那竭國來，時佛<note n="1115030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔般〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note type="mod" n="1115030" resp="CBETA">般【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1115030"><lem wit="【大】">般</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>泥洹已經七日。諸天往
<lb ed="T" n="1115c03"/>赴，悉持天華天香供養佛身，此華即是。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1115c0316" rend="inline">迦葉
<lb ed="T" n="1115c04"/>聞是語，便自投於地啼泣而言：「佛今般泥洹，
<lb ed="T" n="1115c05"/>三界失明，將復何依恃？」<note n="1115031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便帥＝彼師【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115031" type="mod">便帥【大】，彼師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115031"><lem wit="【大】">便帥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">彼師</rdg></app>將諸弟子進
<lb ed="T" n="1115c06"/>道，未到數百里，便見四天王及梵釋諸天，皆
<lb n="1115c07" ed="T"/>持七寶蓋、名香好華，悉<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115032" resp="Taisho">〔往供…諸天〕六字－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115032">（往供…諸天）六字【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="6" n="1115032"><lem wit="【大】">往供養佛，諸天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作
<lb n="1115c08" ed="T"/>十二部音樂，亦有阿須輪王、諸大鬼神側塞
<lb n="1115c09" ed="T"/>空中，又<note resp="Taisho" n="1115033" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝具【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，具【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115033"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">具</rdg></app>俱夷那竭國王及諸隣國王，各
<lb ed="T" n="1115c10"/>從其群僚數百萬人。見迦葉將諸弟子到，是
<lb ed="T" n="1115c11"/>時國貴末羅<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115034">〔弗〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">弗【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115034"><lem wit="【大】">弗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>王，則勅國人民皆令避道，使
<lb n="1115c12" ed="T"/>迦葉及<note resp="Taisho" n="1115035" place="foot text" type="orig">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115035" type="mod">諸【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115035"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>弟子得進。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1115c1209" rend="inline">阿那律出迎相見言：「佛
<lb n="1115c13" ed="T"/>般泥洹已<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115036" resp="Taisho">七＝士【宋】</note><note type="mod" n="1115036" resp="CBETA">七【大】，士【宋】</note><app n="1115036"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">士</rdg></app>日，耶維火不然，但待賢者到
<lb n="1115c14" ed="T"/><note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115037" resp="Taisho">〔耳〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115037" resp="CBETA">耳【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115037"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>！」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1115c1402" rend="inline">阿難見迦葉，便自<note resp="Taisho" n="1115038" place="foot text" type="orig">投＋（此）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115038">投【大】，投此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115038"><lem wit="【大】">投</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">投此</rdg></app>地啼哭不自勝。有
<lb ed="T" n="1115c15"/>一老比丘名波或，即止阿難言：「止止！佛在時
<lb ed="T" n="1115c16"/>常禁制我等，不得自由。佛今<app corresp="#1115030" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">般</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>泥洹，吾等得
<lb n="1115c17" ed="T"/>自在。莫復啼哭。」時有天聞波或語，即舉手搏
<lb n="1115c18" ed="T"/>之，迦葉便前接持，天止之，謂波或言：「佛今般
<lb n="1115c19" ed="T"/>泥洹，一切失所<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115039">恃＝持【宋】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115039">恃【大】，持【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1115039"><lem wit="【大】">恃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">持</rdg></app>，汝獨愚癡而反喜快。」波
<lb n="1115c20" ed="T"/>或聞是語<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1115040" resp="Taisho">意解＝竟【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1115040">意解【大】，竟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115040"><lem wit="【大】">意解</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竟</rdg></app>，即得阿羅漢<note resp="Taisho" n="1115041" place="foot text" type="orig">〔道〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115041"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1115c2013">迦葉便與
<lb n="1115c21" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" n="1115042" place="foot text" type="orig">諸弟子＝弟子俱【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115042" type="mod">諸弟子【大】，弟子俱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115042"><lem wit="【大】">諸弟子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">弟子俱</rdg></app>頭面著地，作禮繞棺三匝<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115043">〔悲哀〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1115043" resp="CBETA">悲哀【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115043"><lem wit="【大】">悲哀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>而
<lb ed="T" n="1115c22"/>言：「我等今日不知佛頭足所在。」<note resp="Taisho" n="1115044" place="foot text" type="orig">（（佛威…佛言））二十七字＝（（即便悲哀而說偈言））八字【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115044a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛威…感傷）十五字【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="15" n="1115044a"><lem wit="【大】">佛威神則為
<lb n="1115c23" ed="T"/>出足，諸天人民莫不感傷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1115c2311" rend="inline"><note n="1115044b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於是摩訶迦葉乃說偈讚佛言【大】，即便悲哀而說偈言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115044b" cb:word-count="27"><lem wit="【大】">於是摩訶迦葉乃
<lb ed="T" n="1115c24"/>說偈讚佛言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">即便悲哀而說偈言</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="1115c25"/><lg xml:id="lgT12p1115c2501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「佛為三界乘，</l><l>度於生死淵，</l>
<lb n="1115c26" ed="T"/><l><note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1115045">澹泊＝憺怕【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1115045" type="mod">澹泊【大】，憺怕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115045"><lem wit="【大】">澹泊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">憺怕</rdg></app>昇泥洹，</l><l>微妙越世間。</l>
<pb xml:id="T12.0393.1116a" n="1116a" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a01"/><l>佛為無量明，</l><l>照於愚癡冥，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a02"/><l>願為一切人，</l><l>顯耀<note n="1116001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現＝見【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1116001" type="mod">現【大】，見【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116001"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>威靈。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a03"/><l>佛為大慈哀，</l><l>所度無央數，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a04"/><l>尊體處金棺，</l><l>清淨寂然安。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a05"/><l>願用優和德，</l><l>見身色相光，</l>
<lb n="1116a06" ed="T"/><l>普令天及人，</l><l>興起無量福。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a07"/><l>佛為開現法，</l><l>眾生受潤澤，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a08"/><l>得止生死輪，</l><l><note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1116002">或＝惑【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1116002">或【大】，惑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116002"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惑</rdg></app>者入正諦，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a09"/><l>已蒙如來恩，</l><l>頭面禮佛足。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a10"/><l>今但覩<note n="1116003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">金棺＝棺槨【三】【宮】</note><note n="1116003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金棺【大】，棺槨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116003"><lem wit="【大】">金棺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">棺槨</rdg></app>，</l><l>心為悲感傷，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a11"/><l>佛雖就無為，</l><l>聖達靡不實。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a12"/><l>見後有疑<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1116004" resp="Taisho">諦＝諍【三】【宮】</note><note n="1116004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諦【大】，諍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116004"><lem wit="【大】">諦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諍</rdg></app>，</l><l>出足於金棺，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a13"/><l>起分是生死，</l><l>佛以不復愁，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="1116a14"/><l>法身慧常存，</l><l>莫呼永泥洹。」</l></lg>
<lb n="1116a15" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="001"><cb:jhead><title>迦葉赴佛<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="1116005" resp="Taisho">〔般〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1116005" resp="CBETA">般【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1116005"><lem wit="【大】">般</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>涅槃經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>